data.description: Charming split-level home boasting 1234 sqft of well-designed space. This residence features elegant hardwood floors, stunning granite counters in the kitchen, and a luxurious tile master tub. Step outside to enjoy the serenity of a covered patio, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Conveniently located close to shopping and entertainment options, this home offers both comfort and accessibility for an ideal lifestyle.
